Get to know what Astar Network is solvin.message: Get to know what Astar Network is solving and all the information related to our native token.

Dive into our ecosystem and discover mor.message: Dive into our ecosystem and discover more about Polkadot, Substrate and other initiatives.

Find all the resources you need in order.message: Find all the resources you need in order to start testing, deploying, and interacting with smart contracts on the network.

Earn tokens for yourself and your dApp b.message: Earn tokens for yourself and your dApp by staking tokens and registering your dApp with Astar’s dApp Staking.

Dive deeper into EVM on Astar and explai.message: Dive deeper into EVM on Astar and explains how EVM contracts can interact with other non-EVM modules through precompiles.

Use all-in-one Swanky Suite to start bui.message: Use all-in-one Swanky Suite to start building WASM smart contracts. Get an overview of ink! and ask! WASM contract frameworks and examples for each framework.

Explain how to run full nodes, collators.message: Explain how to run full nodes, collators, indexers, and everything you need to know related to infrastructure.

Explain how XCM is used in Astar and how.message: Explain how XCM is used in Astar and how developers can use it to interact with the rest of the Polkadot network.

Provide relevant information about the w.message: Provide relevant information about the wallets, bridges, indexers, and oracles that are integrated with the network.

Learn how to create different types of w.message: Learn how to create different types of wallets, obtain tokens, and manage your assets.

Learn how to use tools and build project.message: Learn how to use tools and build projects in Astar ecosystem.
